                <head>202. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On May 16, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_MCR1">McClintock</persName> and
                    Cambodian Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_LN1">Leng Ngeth</persName> signed
                    a bilateral agreement on military assistance on behalf of their respective
                    countries. For text, see TIAS 3240 or 6 UST 995. Documentation on the extensive
                    and largely technical negotiations for the agreement is in Department of State,
                    Central File 751H.5–<gloss target="#t_MSP1">MSP</gloss>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
